headline: Is Constellation Energy’s 47% Rally in 2025 Backed by Fundamentals?
summary: Thinking about what to do with Constellation Energy stock? You are definitely not alone. With the share price having surged almost 10% in just the last week and an impressive 47.3% gain year-to-date, this stock is grabbing attention from investors looking for both growth and stability. The 3-year move is even more jaw-dropping, with Constellation posting a staggering 324.8% return. It is hard to ignore momentum like that. Some of this buzz tracks back to broader shifts in the energy industry...
